name: AirTor Protocol from Ethereum
description: Forked from Ethereum with Pulsechain. Bridged from Ethereum via https://bridge.pulsechain.com. Original Address - 0x0F7B3F5a8FeD821c5eb60049538a548dB2D479ce. ATOR empowers The Onion Router (Tor) through on-chain incentives, and facilitates wider adoption of secure network relay protocols through hardware products.
